Czechs Republic Names Davis Cup Team 
Bohdan Ulihrach, Slava Dosedel, Jiri Novak and David Rikl were on
Monday named for the Czech Republic team to play the Davis Cup World
Group first-round match against Belgium in Gent from April 2-4.
The singles players will be chosen from Ulihrach, Dosedel and Novak
with Rikl included specially as a doubles player.
